{"tid":2130354,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"保就業計劃第6批工資補貼涉47億元　承諾受薪僱員人數約20萬","createTime":"2020-07-29T07:08:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T07:26:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"51b23a2d93523b31bb8bf44f61b0578661ecfa72","tid":2130354,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:08:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540551-20200729.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540551-20200729.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6d6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=3a10e67e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540551-20200729.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3f02bec7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540551-20200729.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n「保就業」計劃發放第6批、超過47億元工資補貼，涉及約11600名僱主，承諾受薪僱員人數約20萬。<br />\n<br />\n「保就業」計劃秘書處表示，將於本周內通知第七批約17300名成功申請的僱主，並於下周向他們發放約64億元工資補貼，承諾受薪僱員人數約28萬3千人。<br />\n<br />\n連同首6批已發放的工資補貼，7批工資補貼合共涉及約405億元，涵蓋接近13萬8千名僱主及承諾受薪僱員總人數超過175萬。秘書處正處理餘下約18300份申請的審批工作。"},{"pid":"fb400d939740ab527d63a220e42a0ed5275baae8","tid":2130354,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:08:41.000Z","msg":"快D出第二期保就業啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b9c7dc9e9cf952818fb9fcc3fb4fcdb9adc71d","tid":2130354,"uid":345516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:09:14.000Z","msg":"反正唔關我事<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mR2qAL2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmR2qAL2.gif&h=2715a5fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee785f2e2dcd5cabc165937f42d89d3a3cc